snippet.title: Robbie Swifthand and the Orb of Mysteries | PC GAMEPLAY | HD 1440P
snippet.description:
Buy games at a great discount!
https://www.g2a.com/r/discountme


//- Info
Robbie Swifthand and the Orb of Mysteries! A hardcore 2D platformer that will mess with your mind and test your skills. Enter a Temple full of devious traps and of course, lots of treasure! 
http://store.steampowered.com/app/718010/Robbie_Swifthand_and_the_Orb_of_Mysteries/


//- Addition
Real fun and fast platformer with some puzzle elements. I had to cut out some of the fails because there is a death around every corner.


//- System Recommendation
OS: Windows 10
Processor: i5 Quadcore or equivalent(3.5ghz or faster)
Memory: 4 GB RAM
Graphics: Nvidia GTX1050
Storage: 1 GB available space
